Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:30.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:37.31,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:44.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:51.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:01:00.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:05.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:10.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:16.48,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:22.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,副船长艾丽朵拉 向娜蒂亚提及自己的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,13年前 她的故乡遭一名男子毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.39,0:01:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并让她失去弟弟与双亲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了向石像鬼以及他的组织 新亚特兰提斯复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才会建造出这艘鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但鹦鹉螺号却即将陷入 石像鬼的陷阱之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:56.14,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#21 再见了…鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目标进入第四区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有如扑火的夏虫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这将是你最后的航海 鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,离克马得海沟还有2000
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发射声纳\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,敌潜自舰首2点至10点钟方向 呈扇状展开 共六艘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,六对一吗…有些棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不光是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰尾两舷应该也有敌人接近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可真是生死存亡的大危机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目标进入第三区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开始D-2计划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 开始计划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长嘴硬鳞鱼6至12号 开始作战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发射管注水音 距离2200
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鱼雷发射音 雷数24枚 距离2000
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这还真是场鱼雷暴雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鱼雷接近 还有60秒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鱼雷防御\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,共有5枚突破弹幕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两舷全速 下降回避
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鱼雷接近 还有20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别理会 尽量沿着海底前进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,4枚通过上方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:03:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有1枚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是船长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是往上方回避 就正中敌方下怀了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,受损情形？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰尾进水 程度极轻微
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长嘴硬鳞鱼号的动静呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 舰首有六艘 右舷两点钟有四艘正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相对速度约8海浬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 准备反击 副船长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全管装填 飞行深水炸弹及诱导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开启发射管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解 开启发射管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飞行深水炸弹朝右舷射出后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,10秒后朝第二目标群 发射诱导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飞行深水炸弹 装填完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,左舷发射管区 完成准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,测距完毕 完成误差修正
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诱导弹全数发射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,确认舰体破坏音 数目为6
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有4艘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,确认舰体破坏音 数目为4
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么一来 就将追踪到的 长嘴硬鳞鱼号全数击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一共有10艘是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,敌人这回可真是大手笔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:06:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,副船长 攻击弹药还剩多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还剩三分之一 目前正重新装填
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其它的长嘴硬鳞鱼号 情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,另外掌握到5艘 但不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正逐渐脱离这个海域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是打算拉开距离 进行鱼雷战吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 似乎远离至射程距离之外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是撤退了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,留心正上方的深水炸弹攻击\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该会有什么从上方过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以影像确认鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进入射程范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫 不好意思 得拿你来测试新武器了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开始超级捕捉作战\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进入作战第二阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备超级捕捉光线炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发射口开启
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,降下光线炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光线炮准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自反重舱传达动力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,磁场安定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,掌握目标
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完成发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发射超级捕捉光线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船舰全体遭到强力磁场覆盖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是超级捕捉光线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼那家伙已经完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫 这下子你还有本事 逃离我的新武器吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船舰正被往上方吸去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:08:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舵向下 后部水槽排气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样舰身将会倒立
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无所谓 只要能脱离磁场范围
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全体人员请做好舰身倾斜准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh  NO！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船究竟在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎全开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,白费力气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,输出功率达80%
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,行不通 还是被吸了上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎室 不能再提高输出功率了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再提高下去 推进器会支撑不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距离海面还有30公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你快在我们面前现身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们正浮在空中？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上空出现巨大飞行物体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这…这东西真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太惊人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,名符其实的空中战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？怎么了？ 发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非战斗员请回避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别那么不知变通嘛 你这个讨厌鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们也有知道目前状况的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们浮在空中耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是因为那块巨大磁铁吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是那艘船 是怎么浮在空中的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原子震动炮及超音波炮 完成固定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进入作战最终阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于可以测试这项传说曾毁灭 耶利哥古城的武器威力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫 这是我送你下地狱的邀请函
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瞄准鹦鹉螺号的宇宙钛金
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,固有频率设定完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能源填充完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全系统一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完成发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对方正在对本舰发射特殊电波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让我们听这种声音做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰首装甲板发生龟裂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰尾、舰底也陆续出现裂痕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是原子震动炮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼那家伙 竟然把这种东西都挖了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看你还能撑到何时 鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰首上甲板 第一装甲板剥离
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主雷达室受损
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长 再这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全弹发射 我们应战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,防护罩是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,靠这艘船的对空武器 根本奈何不了它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一辅助引擎全毁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本就是想把我们 慢慢折磨到死嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第三船舱全毁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火炮弹药库引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火炮管制系统无法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成对消灭引擎出现异常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主电源受损
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,万事休矣是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号完全沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暂停攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,联络鹦鹉螺号 我要跟尼莫通话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,空中战舰来电
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好久不见了 尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你这个混帐啊 石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这种冷淡的态度 还是跟13年前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着你多事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 那也快结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和你的人生一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,13年前的那盘西洋棋 还没和你分出胜负呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不如现在来下完那盘棋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那盘棋胜负已定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你那不服输的个性 也是一点都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很遗憾 我们无法再见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 那也是 和我抱持不同想法的你的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么再会了 尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:14:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的船一同永眠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有其它方法了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有一个赢得胜利的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是个好机会 自爆吧 尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不光是新亚特兰提斯的 空中战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,甚至连石像鬼都在我们面前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这正是让我们完成目标的 千载难逢的好机会不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要立刻引爆成对消灭引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这一切就会全部消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自爆吧 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这13年来我们就是为了这一刻 而活到现在不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还在犹豫什么？尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请做出裁示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以前你绝不会 为了这种事有所迟疑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你变了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我帮你把原因说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是因为娜蒂亚对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为不能杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在胡说八道什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想找死是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但可以请你别把不想死的人 也一起拖下水好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然人在这艘船上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就必须遵从我们的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不论你是怎么想的 但这艘船的存在目的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是为了要消灭新亚特兰提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁理你啊 这个讨厌鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『反正是没指望的感情』
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『不如就与尼莫船长共赴黄泉』
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这才是你的真正想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可是敬谢不敏喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要我就会选择一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再说 我可一点都不想 连婚都还没结
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就陪你一起死！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们两个 走人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们会搭乘葛兰坦离开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟没有义务留在这里一起死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们先别走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算用葛兰坦逃了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是会被那块大磁铁给吸住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这虽然是铁制的 却完全不会被吸过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说 那台机器 只对鹦鹉螺号的超合金反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你们真的要逃走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傻瓜 不那么说的话 我不就太没面子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在尼莫面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可不能让那个讨厌鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和我最重要的尼莫先生 一起殉情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对对对对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到最后关头都不能轻言放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 自杀是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们还是想办法撑到最后一刻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种情况下 还奢望能死里逃生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们只剩下一枚导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,况且也无法开启发射口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种情况下要怎么反击？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 问题在于 要如何脱离目前的险境
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,关于这点\N关于这点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了给予我们最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对方一定会开启 大型诱导弹的发射口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到时候防护罩 一定也会被解除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就瞄准那个瞬间 从这边将导弹打进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么一来 就能在内部引发大爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反击的契机 大概就只有那时了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们根本不晓得 对方发射口的位置在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,关于这点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总得试了才知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要存在着些微可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就该相信 然后放手一搏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用人力…是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就用人力扳开诱导弹发射口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,手头上没事的人 都立刻过去帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有就是该由谁去破坏发射口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就请交给我们来办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们会驾驶葛兰坦出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请趁这段时间掌握反击的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请保重 尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也带我一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行\N为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你得保护娜蒂亚、玛莉和大王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是男人的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听好了 强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所谓的战争 不光是要守护他人 自己也要存活下来才有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你可别死喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那还用得着说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见了 保重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们的人生还真是高潮迭起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 一点都不无聊真是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那也要能继续活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遵命\N遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,改由长嘴硬鳞鱼号 集中火力攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样空中战舰 根本就不会开启发射口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有电力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连这里的舱门都打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无所谓 撞开它就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遵命\N遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,改为飞行模式 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,气球表面铺上了硬化玻陨石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以撑上一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 只剩一发钢铁子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交给你了 桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:19:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可是个射击天才
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这真是射击训练的最佳标靶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 但命中率实在太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非…非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,风速\N6公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,气温\N22度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,气压\N0.94
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距离\N1200
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么这边没铺玻陨石？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没那个时间嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一发子弹就干掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,预备…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们实在太过倚赖 这艘船的机械了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一旦失去电力 就只能落得这种下场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第二垂直引擎中等程度受损
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,右舷居住区 无人回应
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,工作室的情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不晓得 可能已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求求你 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会交出蔚蓝之水 不要再继续互相残杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼大人 是娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她果然在鹦鹉螺号上\N请问要如何处置她？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有意思 娜蒂亚还有利用价值
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把她带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经抓到娜蒂亚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也差不多该将军了\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备发射歼灭导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫的蔚蓝之水之后再慢慢找
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,借助皇帝陛下的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.70,0:22:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰首全毁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是同样的再来一发 我们就玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又再装填弹药了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.98,0:22:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号的舱门还没开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.98,0:22:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.65,0:22:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.65,0:22:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下次发射就是我们的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是能命中就是奇迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.66,0:22:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所谓的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.12,0:22:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是要靠自己的力量来引发的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,击中了\N击中了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救命啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.91,0:23:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,着地漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是现在 发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了 磁力逐渐减弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全员做好冲击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.02,0:23:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非…非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.16,0:23:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目前先全力灭火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.23,0:23:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之后再追究你的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.63,0:23:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.70,0:23:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号受损成那样 也撑不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.50,0:24:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,派长嘴硬鳞鱼号解决它\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.57,0:24:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号正沉入海中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.25,0:24:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是愚蠢之人的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.05,0:24:23.91,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.92,0:24:31.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.93,0:24:37.03,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.10,0:24:41.40,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.48,0:24:50.25,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.32,0:25:00.35,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.43,0:25:09.23,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.30,0:25:13.50,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.57,0:25:18.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.18,0:25:27.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.80,0:25:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.90,0:25:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是…船长室？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.04,0:25:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.44,0:25:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要将这个房间 与主船舱分离
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.21,0:25:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们快离开这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.34,0:25:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你要保护娜蒂亚与玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.82,0:25:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『叛徒艾丽朵拉』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.62,0:25:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要看喔
